   <h2> 海澜之家采用ENLINK SSL VPN解决远程使用NC系统 <a href="forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=9371&amp;page=1&amp;authorid=31720&amp;mobile=2" rel="nofollow" class="blue" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:normal;margin-left:10px;">只看楼主</a> </h2> 
   <div class="plc cl" id="pid33355"> 
    <span class="avatar"><img src="http://bbs.erp100.com/ucenter/avatar.php?uid=31720&amp;size=small" style="width:32px;height:32px;" /></span> 
    <div class="display pi" href="#replybtn_33355"> 
     <ul class="authi"> 
      <li class="grey"> <em> 楼主</em><b> <a href="home.php?mod=space&amp;uid=31720&amp;mobile=2" class="blue">wgjhj</a></b> </li> 
      <li class="grey rela"> <em><a href="home.php?mod=spacecp&amp;ac=favorite&amp;type=thread&amp;id=9371&amp;mobile=2" class="favbtn blue">收藏</a></em> 2007/4/12 09:50:36</li> 
